            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "When lazy loader is true (debug/reloader)\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n$ flask run   \r\n * Serving Flask app \"app.py\" (lazy loading)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen lazy loader is false (eager loader, production, no debug, no reloader)\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n$ flask run                                                                    \r\n * Serving Flask app \"app.py\"\r\n``` \r\n\r\nSo no new message added, only the current message includes explicit warning"
